headline: Hologic (NASDAQ:HOLX) Misses Q4 CY2025 Revenue Estimates
summary: Medical technology company Hologic (NASDAQ:HOLX) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025 as sales rose 2.5% year on year to $1.05 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.04 per share was 5.4% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
